  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Symptomatic and asymptomatic patients wearing Metal on Metal hip prosthesis will be enrolled
      in the study and periimplant pseudotumors will be searched by means of NMR (Nuclear Magnetic
      Resonance).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
