      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients wearing MoM hip prosthesis

          -  Head &gt;= 36 mm

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence of ferromagnetic implants and/or presence of clinical situations that are not
